headline: Cavallo Expands SalesPad eCommerce Capabilities to Strengthen Omnichannel Distribution Support
summary: Cavallo, the Profit Maximization leader for distributors, today announced enhanced eCommerce capabilities for its SalesPad distribution management software, with new connectors for Shopify, WooCommerce, and Adobe Commerce. These enhancements reflect Cavallo's continued investment in supporting SalesPad customers and bringing online workflows in line with the operational power distributors rely on every day.

headline: E-Commerce Update - Retail Media Networks Surge Transforming Shopper Engagement
summary: The Retail Media Networks (RMN) market is exhibiting substantial growth, projected to reach USD 7.3 billion by 2034, driven by a 20% compound annual growth rate (CAGR) from 2025 to 2034. This expansion is fueled by retailer-brand collaborations that utilize customer data for personalized ad experiences, enhancing the shopping journey across various touchpoints, including online and in-store channels.
